A simple video library system using packedobjectsd library. The client broadcasts new video release information to subscribed searchers at default frequency. The client will init_packedobjectsd using the video.xsd schema and responder flag. The searcher will init_packedobjectsd using the video.xsd schema and searcher flag. The searcher will wait for data from clients.

To run the program, first compile and install the packedobjectsd library using autoconf tools and then compile this program using autoconf tools. Run video_searcher and then video_client.